{"tid":1282283,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"失望！譚校長真是人模狗樣的東西！","createTime":"2019-07-03T14:03:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-04T13:19:33.000Z","uid":203071,"like":61,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4a8b7b961af3875cab3cc50ead408244dd8dee41","tid":1282283,"uid":203071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T14:03:47.000Z","msg":"周柏豪琴晚喺instagram提醒大家記得登記做選民，唔上微博都唔知，原來登記做選民行使公民權利同責任都係支持港獨㗎！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8AoHZDb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8AoHZDb.png&h=597c46f5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f0yAAbw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff0yAAbw.png&h=5018b509&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9eKPED9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9eKPED9.png&h=665f761c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我對比比鳥真係好失望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係同時間！！！<br />\n我發現我最鍾意嘅譚詠麟竟然都呼籲過選民去投票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/LrXlB_UED1E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FLrXlB_UED1E&d=3FtZuWe%2BwKi7N9uEGSTnHoc%2FDYnbIFO1z8NzTSvCTwQ%3D&h=cdfcab39\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/LrXlB_UED1E</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/uILiXcNneug\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FuILiXcNneug&d=3FtZuWe%2BwKi7N9uEGSTnHoc%2FDYnbIFO1z8NzTSvCTwQ%3D&h=a24d08b9\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/uILiXcNneug</a><br />\n<br />\n伦伯點可以一邊得到中国人民同伦迷嘅支持，另一邊呼籲市民去投票！咪即係變相支持港獨？點可以背棄內地無得投票嘅同胞呼籲香港人投票！伦伯原來係個双面人！人模狗样的东西！請大家唔好再支持佢！實在太令人失望！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> btw2019區議會選舉將於11月24日舉行，雖然有啲早，但大家記得話俾屋企嘅三姑六婆知，唔好再食住蛇齋餅糭去支持港獨喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />食窮佢好喇唔好跟人去投呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>有票記得投！自己香港自己救！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong>"},{"pid":"bb2b34ce475847a0af5616c9cf7fda8439e6ab70","tid":1282283,"uid":203071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T14:09:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07a26970b5235ae63a030a8f88f8c6b26e444b92","tid":1282283,"uid":203071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T14:09:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ec1668a95ad7a96d2acf4cbb3b69405ee1e0a91","tid":1282283,"uid":203071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T14:11:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03ff4c051695c4c4afa3e58c84341e2f0b103f68","tid":1282283,"uid":203071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T01:41:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a6bcb4f08369d78ac3c26eacebacf0b0d694d0f","tid":1282283,"uid":33640,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T01:45:04.000Z","msg":"叫人登記做選民都比人屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89b13941db77b94b62dd10ec4deb133bafab7bf0","tid":1282283,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T02:32:29.00